## Agile/Scrum Implementation Workflow

Set up or run an agile process:

- [ ] 1. Team setup: Define team structure, roles ({{team_roles}}), and capacity
- [ ] 2. Backlog creation: Build initial backlog from {{project_requirements}}
- [ ] 3. Sprint planning: Plan sprint goals and commitments ({{sprint_length}})
- [ ] 4. Daily operations: Run standups and manage blockers
- [ ] 5. Review and retrospective: Demonstrate outputs and improve processes
- [ ] 6. Velocity tracking: Measure and forecast using velocity data

## Inputs
- Team size: {{team_size}}
- Sprint length: {{sprint_length}}
- Working days: {{working_days}}
